item.title: CVE-2019-1314|2024-08-04T18:13:30.449Z -- microsoft -- windows%2010%20mobile
item.description: A security feature bypass vulnerability exists in Windows 10 Mobile when Cortana allows a user to access files and folders through the locked screen, aka 'Windows 10 Mobile Security Feature Bypass Vulnerability'.
